area_description_data.5: Both sales and rental prices in 1929 were off about 20% from 1925-28 peak. Location of property within this area will justify policy of holding for its value.

area_description_data.1c: Residents of area required to pay moderate school tuition if students attend city schools (usually pertains only to high school students). Bus transportation available only to north edge.
area_description_data.1b: Highly restricted. Near two high grade country clubs. in valley south of Red Mountain; hence protected from industrial ordors and noises of city. Outside of city limits; zeeshan therefore subject to lower taxation. One of the community's newest localities. Large lots; well landscaped. Layout of community adds charm and appeal. Community stores. Schools.
